  "remarks": "TAi.095 Title: Maulavi. Designation: Governor of Jawzjan Province under the Taliban regime. Member of the Taliban Gerd-e-Jangal Shura and Head of the Taliban Prisoners and Refugees Committee. Belongs to Ishaqzai tribe. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 1822 (2008) was concluded on 23 Jul. 2010; Listing: Listed by UN 1267 Committee on 25 January 2001 (amended on 21 Sep 2007, 29 Nov. 2011)",
